gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Rockets 112, Kings 104
gameRecap.excerpt: The Rockets defeated the Kings, 112-104. Fred VanVleet notched 22 points, four rebounds and nine assists for the Rockets, while Jalen Green added 19 points and three assists in the victory. Domantas Sabonis tallied 25 points, 15 rebounds and eight assists for the Kings in the losing effort. The Rockets improve to 29-35 on the season, while the Kings fall to 36-27.
